name: Ela Gingasha
description:
i am a very good and onest woman, friendly and with a great sence of humor, happy and optimist, romantic, loving and caring.
I am communicative, can easy find common language with any person. I dont like arguments. I do like to smile all the time. I have many good qualities as a person but to write that I am so good will is not correct as it will be not objective. I am tender, sweet.
In my free time I like to watch around the nature, discover new things. I like traveling. In my spare time I like spending time outside. I also like to make photographs, to read interesting self-developing books.
Discovering something new is very exciting to me. I want to find the person who will share my points of view, my life positions. Well, speaking about my ideal man I dont think that he exists in reality. As any person I have his image in my head but he doesnt have bad habits. In our life that is almost impossible. So I want to find common man with common desires, not millionaire, that one who can make me happy and with who I will feel comfortable and good. He must be caring, loving, leader. I like man who is really a man and for me this is leader. I want someone to take care of me. I want relations to be equal in everything.
